    "body": "I have been maintaining Geth nodes for my company projects for over 2 years, \"Head state missing\" status can run over days or even weeks. It always happen when you restart nodes with ancient chain data. I suggest you to download the latest client and sync from scratch is a much better option. For your reference, I sync'ed a new node with Geth v1.10.19 client on AWS t3.xlarge EC2 instance within 12 hours two days ago.",
