    "body": "> For all those reading this in the future, hope your node doesnt randomly lose power for w/e reason what so ever\r\n\r\nI have been maintaining Geth nodes for over 2 years and I really feel your pain.\r\nAll the docs and feedback do not tell how painful and the necessary skills/hardware to maintain long running, highly robust Geth nodes.\r\nMy company now maintains 4 Geth nodes with AWS EC2 instance for daily use and also paying 3rd party blockchain SaaS infrastructure as backup service to maintain 7x24 operations.\r\nWe also re-sync half of our nodes from scratch on every Geth release in case any problem occurs when we restart and upgrade our nodes. (which always happens 🤷‍♂️)",
